        <h1 id="project-gutenberg-needs-your-donation">Project Gutenberg Needs Your Donation</h1>

<p>Thank you for considering a donation to Project Gutenberg.</p>

<p>Think of this as a contribution to later generations. These are remarkable times, and it is good to include you as part of the story.  The <a href="/about/pglaf.html">Project Gutenberg Literary Archive Foundation</a> is registered as a 501(c)(3) charity under the United States Internal Revenue Code, so your donation is tax-deductible to the extent permitted by law.</p>

